com.addicticks.net.httpsupload

Enum Utils.HttpStatusCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Utils.HttpStatusCode>
      • com.addicticks.net.httpsupload.Utils.HttpStatusCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Utils.HttpStatusCode>
    Enclosing class:
    Utils

    public static enum Utils.HttpStatusCode
extends Enum<Utils.HttpStatusCode>
    HTTP Response Status code (with text explanation)

    These are similar to the HTTP-codes found in HttpURLConnection however here they are represented as an enum and come with text as well. Also a few status codes that were missing in the JDK have been added (such as HTTP_CONTINUE).
